ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR RESEARCH USE:

This software implements quantum field dynamics (QFD) simulations for lepton 
physics research. If you use this software in academic research that results 
in publications, please cite:

QFD Phoenix: Production-Ready Lepton Physics Simulations
Quantum Field Dynamics, Tracy McSheery (2025)
https://github.com/qfd-research/phoenix-refactored

The physics methods implemented herein are based on current results 
achieved in electron and muon g-2 predictions within ~9.5% of experimental 
values using the Phoenix Core Hamiltonian approach.